            <p>Email: p.sdh@hnue.edu.vn - Phone: 024.6296.2496</p>
            <p>Website: http://sdh.hnue.edu.vn/ </p>
            <p>Địa chỉ: Tầng 4 Nhà Hiệu bộ - 136 Xuân Thuỷ - Cầu Giấy - Hà Nội</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div id="divProcessing" style="position:fixed;top:0px; left:0px; height:100%;width :100%;text-align:center;
         background:#f5f5f5;
         opacity:0.5;
         z-index:999;
         position:absolute;
         left:0px;
         top :0px;
         cursor: wait; display:none">
    <img style="position: absolute;top: 50%;" src="~/Images/processing.gif" alt="" width="70" height="70" />
</div>
<script>
    function LoadProcess() {
        $('#divProcessing').show();
    }
</script>